message.body: Are you stopping by to get stuffing

Ok that you are giving it for both of us. She didn't answer me yet

What time

Ok about how many ravioli do you want

Ok. I know I have all my college degrees. But I don't remember taking my high school stuff from you

Wont be Done*** until midnight
Well I wait if you want me to because I made the ravioli for you I made 30 of them for you Ame steph
